name: Frog Tank
description:
You have made it to level 99. You just need one more level. Can you do it? Watch out for that net.

Controls-
-Left click "Just Do It" to Begin
-Left click frog to jump
-Right click to change direction
-Press E to extend your tongue
(Eat the fish food to gain experience)

-Made for the 72 hour MiniGam79.
